<doc id="90012" wikidata="Q7205002" url="?curid=90012" title="Pliny, West Virginia">
<text>Pliny is an unincorporated community in Putnam County, West Virginia, United States. It was named for M. Pliny Brown, an early settler. The ZIP code is 25158.

Located near Pliny is Maplewood, listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 2000.

== Notable person ==
* Virginia Mae Brown, set many &quot;first woman&quot; records

